meta.description: This dataset contains core data, primarily from the DECADES data system on the FAAM aircraft. This covers meteorological, chemistry, aerosol, inertial, and airframe measurements.

attributes.acknowledgement: Airborne data was obtained using the BAe-146-301 Atmospheric Research Aircraft [ARA] flown by Airtask Ltd and managed by FAAM Airborne Laboratory, jointly operated by UKRI and the University of Leeds
attributes.creator_address: Building 146, Cranfield University, College Road, Cranfield, Bedford. MK43 0AL. UK.
